    "body": "@aghamir The basefee will change all the time.\r\n\r\nBefore 1559, the gasprice limit is applied to the tip(legacy gasprice) which is straightforward. But after 1559, the semantic of `--gpo.maxprice` **shouldn't** change, it should still applied to the maximum value users want to pay. But right now it's only applied to tip, basefee is ignored.\r\n\r\nI will send a PR to fix it very soon, thanks for the report and sorry for your loss.",
